cms.query.QueryText: SELECT ##COLUMNS## FROM Analytics_Statistics, ##HITSTABLE## WHERE StatisticsSiteID=@SiteID AND StatisticsCode LIKE @CodeName AND StatisticsID=HitsStatisticsID AND HitsStartTime >= @StartTime AND HitsEndTime <= @EndTime AND (StatisticsObjectCulture IS NULL OR StatisticsObjectCulture = '' OR StatisticsObjectCulture = @Culture OR @Culture = '' OR @Culture IS NULL) AND (##WHERE##)
